-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
README to Automate Word Search on Collins ENG-HINDI Dictionary Using Selenium WebDriver for Google Chrome
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Important Note : Please check the usage policy of 'https://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english-hindi' before using it.

=================================
Install the selenium web driver:
-> pip install selenium

=================================

====================================================================================================
Download the latest version of Google ChromeDriver from 'http://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads'
Extract and paste the driver in the current directory.
====================================================================================================


==============================================================
Command:
-> python script_name.py <input_file> <output_file>

Replace script_name.py with the name of the script given above.
===============================================================